AGENT == "A③ Schema + Policy + ToolPack" ==> GUARD
GUARD == "A④ 真实反馈后 UI / TTS 答复" ==> UI
GUARD --> SUP
GUARD --> MOTION
SUP == "B① 高层巡逻命令" ==> PATROL
PATROL == "B② NavigateToPose" ==> NAV
NAV == "B③ /cmd_vel" ==> BASEDRV
BASEDRV == "B④ 轮速 / 里程计闭环" ==> DRIVE
DRIVE --> BASEDRV
BASEDRV --> EKF
SENSORS --> SENSORDRV
SENSORDRV --> SLAM
SENSORDRV --> EKF
SLAM --> NAV
EKF --> NAV
SENSORS --> ZEDSYS
ZEDSYS --> PER
SENSORS --> VOICE
SENSORS --> UI
MB --> MAPMGR
MAPMGR == "C① confirm_default：本地生效" ==> LOCALMAP
MAPMGR == "C② HTTPS 地图上传 / heartbeat" ==> PLATFORM
PLATFORM == "C③ 审核、路线发布、Deployment 下发" ==> MAPMGR
MAPMGR == "C④ 哈希校验与原子安装" ==> LOCALDB
LOCALDB --> PATROL
PLATFORM --> CLOUDDATA

